      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This collection consists of the master file of James J.
         Kilpatrick's columns "A Conservative View," 1979 and
         1990-1992, and "The Writer's Art," 1981-1986, and 1990-1992.
         The "A Conservative View" columns were interfiled with the
         columns in 6626-p, leaving only "The Writer's Art" column
         master file in 6626-q.</p>
      </scopecontent>
